12#pragma once
13
14#include <inttypes.h>
15#include <stdbool.h>
16
17#if !defined(__has_feature)
18#define __has_feature(x) 0
19#endif
20
21#if !defined(__has_extension)
22#define __has_extension(x) __has_feature(x)
23#endif
24
25#if !defined(__GNUC_PREREQ__)
26#if defined(__GNUC__) && defined(__GNUC_MINOR__)
27#define __GNUC_PREREQ__(maj, min) \
28 ((__GNUC__ << 16) + __GNUC_MINOR__ >= ((maj) << 16) + (min))
29#else
30#define __GNUC_PREREQ__(maj, min) 0
31#endif
32#endif
33
34#if !defined(__CLANG_ATOMICS) && !defined(__GNUC_ATOMICS)
35#if __has_extension(c_atomic) || __has_extension(cxx_atomic)
36#define __CLANG_ATOMICS
37#elif __GNUC_PREREQ__(4, 7) || defined(__lint__)
38#define __GNUC_ATOMICS
39#elif !defined(__GNUC__)
40#error "isc/stdatomic.h does not support your compiler"
41#endif
42#endif
43
44#ifndef __ATOMIC_RELAXED
45#define __ATOMIC_RELAXED 0
46#endif
47#ifndef __ATOMIC_CONSUME
48#define __ATOMIC_CONSUME 1
49#endif
50#ifndef __ATOMIC_ACQUIRE
51#define __ATOMIC_ACQUIRE 2
52#endif
53#ifndef __ATOMIC_RELEASE
54#define __ATOMIC_RELEASE 3
55#endif
56#ifndef __ATOMIC_ACQ_REL
57#define __ATOMIC_ACQ_REL 4
58#endif
59#ifndef __ATOMIC_SEQ_CST
60#define __ATOMIC_SEQ_CST 5
61#endif
62
63
64enum memory_order {
65 memory_order_relaxed = __ATOMIC_RELAXED,
66 memory_order_consume = __ATOMIC_CONSUME,
67 memory_order_acquire = __ATOMIC_ACQUIRE,
68 memory_order_release = __ATOMIC_RELEASE,
69 memory_order_acq_rel = __ATOMIC_ACQ_REL,
70 memory_order_seq_cst = __ATOMIC_SEQ_CST
71};
72
73typedef enum memory_order memory_order;
74
75typedef int_fast32_t atomic_int_fast32_t;
76typedef uint_fast32_t atomic_uint_fast32_t;
77typedef int_fast64_t atomic_int_fast64_t;
78typedef uint_fast64_t atomic_uint_fast64_t;
79typedef bool atomic_bool;
80
81#if defined(__CLANG_ATOMICS) /* __c11_atomic builtins */
82#define atomic_init(obj, desired) \
83 __c11_atomic_init(obj, desired)
84#define atomic_load_explicit(obj, order) \
85 __c11_atomic_load(obj, order)
86#define atomic_store_explicit(obj, desired, order) \
87 __c11_atomic_store(obj, desired, order)
88#define atomic_fetch_add_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
89 __c11_atomic_fetch_add(obj, arg, order)
90#define atomic_fetch_sub_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
91 __c11_atomic_fetch_sub(obj, arg, order)
92#define atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
93 __c11_atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail)
94#define atomic_compare_exchange_weak_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
95 __c11_atomic_compare_exchange_weak_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail)
96#elif defined(__GNUC_ATOMICS) /* __atomic builtins */
97#define atomic_init(obj, desired) \
98 (*obj = desired)
99#define atomic_load_explicit(obj, order) \
100 __atomic_load_n(obj, order)
101#define atomic_store_explicit(obj, desired, order) \
102 __atomic_store_n(obj, desired, order)
103#define atomic_fetch_add_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
104 __atomic_fetch_add(obj, arg, order)
105#define atomic_fetch_sub_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
106 __atomic_fetch_sub(obj, arg, order)
107#define atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
108 __atomic_compare_exchange_n(obj, expected, desired, 0, succ, fail)
109#define atomic_compare_exchange_weak_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
110 __atomic_compare_exchange_n(obj, expected, desired, 1, succ, fail)
111#else /* __sync builtins */
112#define atomic_init(obj, desired) \
113 (*obj = desired)
114#define atomic_load_explicit(obj, order) \
115 __sync_fetch_and_add(obj, 0)
116#define atomic_store_explicit(obj, desired, order) \
117 do { \
118 __sync_synchronize(); \
119 *obj = desired; \
120 __sync_synchronize(); \
121 } while (0);
122#define atomic_fetch_add_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
123 __sync_fetch_and_add(obj, arg)
124#define atomic_fetch_sub_explicit(obj, arg, order) \
125 __sync_fetch_and_sub(obj, arg, order)
126#define atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
127 ({ \
128 __typeof__(obj) __v; \
129 _Bool __r; \
130 __v = (__typeof__(obj))__sync_val_compare_and_swap(obj, \
131 *(expected), \
132 desired); \
133 __r = ((__typeof__(obj))*(expected) == __v); \
134 *(expected) = __v; \
135 __r; \
136 })
137#define atomic_compare_exchange_weak_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail) \
138 atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, succ, fail)
139#endif
140
141#define atomic_load(obj) \
142 atomic_load_explicit(obj, memory_order_seq_cst)
143#define atomic_store(obj, arg) \
144 atomic_store_explicit(obj, arg, memory_order_seq_cst)
145#define atomic_fetch_add(obj, arg) \
146 atomic_fetch_add_explicit(obj, arg, memory_order_seq_cst)
147#define atomic_fetch_sub(obj, arg) \
148 atomic_fetch_sub_explicit(obj, arg, memory_order_seq_cst)
149#define atomic_compare_exchange_strong(obj, expected, desired) \
150 atomic_compare_exchange_strong_explicit(obj, expected, desired, memory_order_seq_cst, memory_order_seq_cst)
151#define atomic_compare_exchange_weak(obj, expected, desired) \
152 atomic_compare_exchange_weak_explicit(obj, expected, desired, memory_order_seq_cst, memory_order_seq_cst)
